SIT330-770 Distinction Task 2.2D — Experiment Repository
Copyright (c) 2026 Hashem , Deakin University

This repository contains coursework submitted for academic assessment in
SIT330-770 (Master's Natural Language Processing) at Deakin University.

ACADEMIC USE NOTICE

The code in this repository (Python scripts in code/, scripts/, and paper/)
is released under the MIT License (below) for reproducibility and educational
use. Reviewers, replicators, and other students are welcome to read, run,
adapt, and learn from the pipeline.

The data files (generations.jsonl, evaluations.jsonl, codings, snapshots)
are released as evidence of the experiment having been executed. Their
content includes verbatim API responses from OpenRouter-hosted models
(ChatGPT-4o, Gemini 2.5 Flash, Claude Sonnet 4, Qwen 2.5 72B) and is shared
for academic-replication purposes only. Redistribution of the model outputs
may be subject to those providers' terms of service.

The paper (paper/introduction.pdf, paper/introduction.tex) is the author's
submitted coursework. All rights reserved by the author; no part may be
reproduced or submitted as another's work.

